ia:Protection policy#semi|alt=Page semi-protected|This article is semi-protected.]]"}}'/><link rel="mw:PageProp/Category" href="./Category:Wikipedia_indefinitely_semi-protected_pages#Zoroastrianism" about="#mwt1" id="mwBA"/></p>
