yce_1979_175-58"><a href="./Zoroastrianism#cite_ref-Boyce_1979_175_58-0" rel="mw:referencedBy"><span class="mw-linkback-text">↑ </span></a> <span id="mw-reference-text-cite_note-Boyce_1979_175-58" class="mw-reference-text"><a rel="mw:WikiLink" href="./Zoroastrianism#CITEREFBoyce1979" about="#mwt188" typeof="mw:Transclusion" data-mw='{"parts":[{"template":{"target":{"wt":"harvnb","href":"./Template:Harvnb"},"params":{"1":{"wt":"Boyce"},"2":{"wt":"1979"},"p":{"wt":"175"}},"i":0}}]}' id="mwBFc">Boyce 1979</a><span about="#mwt188" id="mwBFg">, p.</span><span typeof="mw:Entity" about="#mwt188" id="mwBFk"> </span><span about="#mwt188" id="mwBFo">175</span>.</span></li><li about="#cite_note-59" id="cite_note-59"><a href="./Zoroastrianism#cite_ref-59" rel="mw:referencedBy"><span class="mw-linkback-text">↑ </span></a> <span id="mw-reference-text-cite_note-59" class="mw-reference-text"><cite class="citation web" about="#mwt193" typeof="mw:Transclusion" data-mw='{"parts":[{"template":{"target":{"wt":"cite web","href":"./Template:Cite_web"},"params":{"url":{"wt":"http://www.iranicaonline.org/articles/conversion-vii"},"title":{"wt":"CONVERSION vii. Zoroastrian faith in mod. per. – Encyclopaedia Iranica"},"website":{"wt":"Iranicaonline.org"},"date":{"wt":""},"accessdate":{"wt":"2017-06-14"}},"i":0}}]}' id="mwBFs"><a rel="mw:ExtLink" class="external text" href="http://www.iranicaonline.org/articles/conversion-vii" id="mwBFw">"CONVERSION vii. Zoroastrian faith in mod. per. – Encyclopaedia Iranica"</a>. <i id="mwBF0">Iranicaonline.org</i><span class="reference-accessdate" id="mwBF4">. Retrieved <span class="nowrap" id="mwBF8">2017-06-14</span></span>.</cite><span title="ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Ajournal&amp;rft.genre=unknown&amp;rft.jtitle=Iranicaonline.org&amp;rft.atitle=CONVERSION+vii.+Zoroastrian+faith+in+mod.+per.+%E2%80%93+Encyclopaedia+Iranica&amp;rft_id=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.iranicaonline.org%2Farticles%2Fconversion-vii&amp;rfr_id=info%3Asid%2Fen.wikipedia.org%3AZoroastrianism" class="Z3988" about="#mwt193" id="mwBGA"></span><link rel="mw-deduplicated-inline-style" href="mw-data:TemplateStyles:r879151008" about="#mwt193" typeof="mw:Extension/templatestyles" data-mw='{"name":"templatestyles","attrs":{"src":"Module:Citation/CS1/styles.css"},"body":{"extsrc":""}}' id="mwBGE"/></span></li><li about="#cite_note-60" id="cite_note-60"><a href="./Zoroastrianism#cite_ref-60" rel="mw:referencedBy"><span class="mw-linkback-text">↑ </span></a> <span id="mw-reference-text-cite_note-60" class="mw-reference-text">Anne Sofie Roald, Anh Nga Longva. <a rel="mw:ExtLink" class="external text" href="https://books.google.nl/books?id=Ab0yAQAAQBAJ&amp;pg=PA313&amp;dq=armenians+were+zoroastrian&amp;hl=nl&amp;sa=X&amp;ved=0CEYQ6AEwBWoVChMI49KPt6KSxgIVAo4sCh1evgDN#v=onepage&amp;q=armenians%20were%20zoroastrian&amp;f=false" id="mwBGI"><i id="mwBGM">Religious Minorities in the Middle East: Domination, Self-Empowerment, Accommodation</i></a> Brill, 2011, <link rel="mw-deduplicated-inline-style" href="mw-data:TemplateStyles:r879151008" about="#mwt196" typeof="mw:Extension/templatestyles mw:Transclusion" data-mw='{"parts":[{"template":{"target":{"wt":"ISBN","href":"./Template:ISBN"},"params":{"1":{"wt":"9004216847"}},"i":0}}]}' id="mwBGQ"/><a rel="mw:WikiLink" href="./International_Standard_Book_Number" title="International Standard Book Number" about="#mwt196" id="mwBGU">ISBN</a><span typeof="mw:Entity" about="#mwt196" id="mwBGY"> </span><a rel="mw:WikiLink" href="./Special:BookSources/9004216847" title="Special:BookSources/9004216847" about="#mwt196" id="mwBGc">9004216847</a>, p. 313</span></li><li about="#cite_note-parsikhabar.net-61" id="cite_note-parsikhabar.net-61"><a href="./Zoroastrianism#cite_ref-parsikhabar.net_61-0" rel="mw:referencedBy"><span class="mw-linkback-text">↑ </span></a> <span id="mw-reference-text-cite_note-parsikhabar.net-61" class="mw-reference-text"><cite class="citation web" about="#mwt208" typeof="mw:Tran